// "Popular" surface; first 8 are pre-shown via INDUSTRIES_VISIBLE).
// The remaining ~330 entries are niche-level variants, each mapped to
// one of the parent keys so downstream filters (SUGGESTIONS_BY_INDUSTRY,
// SERVICES_BY_INDUSTRY, TAGLINES_BY_INDUSTRY) keep working when a niche
// is picked. The substring filter in IndustryCombobox handles the rest.
